{"tid":2190141,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩推動到你做尖？","createTime":"2020-09-05T11:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T06:42:16.000Z","uid":158760,"like":28,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"9881aa473f62426693d312d882194a65e0b84858","tid":2190141,"uid":158760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"做尖做到上晒癮，但點解會咁上癮呢⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n溝女？真心唔覺得有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵錢？大隻左又唔會搵到錢，反而洗多左錢就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n健康？搵到三餐食已經好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n踏入第6個月做gym既生活，唔知點解自己會keep住去，唔知去黎做乜，但從來都冇諗過cut membership。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每晚放工返到屋企就已經開始諗今晚做咩動作做幾多set幾時飲pre workout幾時飲whey，supplement 其實唔重要，但飲完再做gym又唔知點解會莫名其妙地興奮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">到底點解我會繼續做gym?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n毒到盡頭就會想健康？我自己都唔知⋯⋯自信？<br />\n<br />\n（其實想cut都cut唔到，但冇諗住cut）"},{"pid":"5137f65332631bcb165b4c0b7f3462b9e68a57bd","tid":2190141,"uid":180156,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:44:34.000Z","msg":"做咗3個月已經無動力<br />\n我純粹要將唔鐘意做嘅事都要做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca5631e16f963a11b9700576400a505f9052683","tid":2190141,"uid":188374,"like":21,"dislike":21,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"D細路夠鍾意打機啦 興趣黎姐<br />\n做GYM一定好過打機呢d垃圾活動"},{"pid":"7939430175a77f690fa75bd7efb6c98f412c8424","tid":2190141,"uid":103248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"溝仔"},{"pid":"57b33d865350ded5fd5c61849b039d29790de175","tid":2190141,"uid":158760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5137f65332631bcb165b4c0b7f3462b9e68a57bd","tid":2190141,"uid":180156,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:44:34.000Z","msg":"做咗3個月已經無動力<br />\n我純粹要將唔鐘意做嘅事都要做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:58:48.000Z","msg":"但冇動力點keep住去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e722f8e2f2f7430033200da4c4646e44a58296","tid":2190141,"uid":158760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fca5631e16f963a11b9700576400a505f9052683","tid":2190141,"uid":188374,"like":21,"dislike":21,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"D細路夠鍾意打機啦 興趣黎姐<br />\n做GYM一定好過打機呢d垃圾活動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"又唔好話垃圾<br />\n商機黎架 E-Sport呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打機打到有糧出，其實同做運動員做到有糧出，冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問自己一句：如果打機有糧出，你做唔做先，有冇興趣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5df09627a0acb44c65f86e62b4216408561bf0","tid":2190141,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:01:35.000Z","msg":"為左自己"},{"pid":"c05003dcd7510db498e2902ec53d6f5c652a9610","tid":2190141,"uid":119756,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"5e8ce87a275629f76e52767299bfe6f2d31499bc","tid":2190141,"uid":28845,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:03:47.000Z","msg":"鍾意喺健身室入面逃離現實既壓力，其實同鐘意打機一樣咁姐。但健身仲帶黎健康同自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54b58edb66ee6a0c27ebc22aa1eb8f1688ce908","tid":2190141,"uid":167692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c05003dcd7510db498e2902ec53d6f5c652a9610","tid":2190141,"uid":119756,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"721"},"citedBy